{"id":8173,"date":"2026-02-02T11:50:00","date_gmt":"2026-02-02T04:50:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=8173"},"modified":"2026-02-02T11:50:01","modified_gmt":"2026-02-02T04:50:01","slug":"zinc-oxide-zno-mang-loc-vat-ly","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/xu-huong\/zinc-oxide-zno-mang-loc-vat-ly\/","title":{"rendered":"Zinc Oxide (ZnO) \u2013 M\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc v\u1eadt l\u00fd, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Zinc Oxide l\u00e0 m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc v\u1eadt l\u00fd: che ph\u1ee7 UVA\/UVB \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, dung n\u1ea1p t\u1ed1t, gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u\/solvent. Nh\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n l\u00e0 white cast (v\u1ec7t tr\u1eafng); tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00e1c c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 h\u1ea1t nano\/non-nano hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 t\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9.<\/span><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"gioi-thieu-chung-ve-zinc-oxide\"><\/span><b>Gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u chung v\u1ec1 Zinc Oxide<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>T\u00ean khoa h\u1ecdc\/INCI:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Zinc Oxide (ZnO). Thu\u1ed9c nh\u00f3m m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc kho\u00e1ng\/v\u1eadt l\u00fd.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Ngu\u1ed3n g\u1ed1c \u2013 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> ZnO \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ee9ng d\u1ee5ng h\u00e0ng th\u1ebf k\u1ef7 trong d\u01b0\u1ee3c (m\u1ee1 k\u1ebdm, h\u0103m t\u00e3) nh\u1edd t\u00ednh l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu \u2013 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7. Trong m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng, ZnO n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u00ec ph\u1ed5 UVA r\u1ed9ng\u2014\u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh m\u00e0 Titanium Dioxide (TiO\u2082) \u0111\u01a1n l\u1ebb kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Vai tr\u00f2 trong KCN:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> T\u1ea1o l\u00e1 ch\u1eafn broad-spectrum (UVA1\/UVA2\/UVB), B\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, sau th\u1ee7 thu\u1eadt, da tr\u1ebb em.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dac-diem-hoat-chat-zinc-oxide\"><\/span><b>\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m ho\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t Zinc Oxide<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cong-dung-noi-bat-cua-zinc-oxide\"><\/span><b>C\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt c\u1ee7a Zinc Oxide<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><b>Ph\u1ed5 r\u1ed9ng th\u1ef1c th\u1ee5:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> bao ph\u1ee7 <\/span><b>UVB + UVA2 + UVA1<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">; n\u00e2ng <\/span><b>PA\/PPD<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 khi d\u00f9ng \u1edf n\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ee7 cao.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>B\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n stabilizer ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc h\u1eefu c\u01a1.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><b>D\u1ecbu da:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> ZnO c\u00f3 t\u00ednh <\/span><b>l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu\/kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam nh\u1eb9<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">, th\u01b0\u1eddng d\u1ec5 dung n\u1ea1p \u1edf da \u0111\u1ecf, k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>\u00cdt g\u00e2y d\u1ecb \u1ee9ng m\u00f9i\/solvent:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c cho da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m ho\u1eb7c d\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"co-che-hoat-dong-cua-zinc-oxide\"><\/span><b>C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Zinc Oxide\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8174\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8174\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8174 size-full\" style=\"font-size: 16px\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/90-1.webp\" alt=\"C\u01a1 ch\u1ebf ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a Zinc Oxide\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/90-1.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/90-1-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/90-1-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/90-1-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8174\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1c m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc v\u1eadt l\u00fd c\u00f3 t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng ch\u1eb7n ph\u1ea7n l\u1edbn tia UV<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><b>T\u00e1n x\u1ea1 + ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 + h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> h\u1ea1t ZnO t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1c v\u1edbi tia UV r\u1ed3i <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1\/t\u00e1n x\u1ea1, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi h\u1ea5p th\u1ee5 v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n ho\u00e1 th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7t \u1edf m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>K\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ea1t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 n\u00ean t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u k\u1ef9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi mua:<\/b><\/p>\n<p><b>Non-nano (\u2265100 nm):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> white cast cao h\u01a1n, c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c d\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Nano (~20\u2013100 nm):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> trong su\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 t\u1ed1t; c\u1ea7n <\/span><b>x\u1eed l\u00fd b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> (silica\/alumina\/stearate) \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf sinh ROS tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t h\u1ea1t v\u00e0 k\u1ebft t\u1ee5.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"zinc-oxide-huong-co-trong-dang-kcn-nao-ket-hop-toi-uu\"><\/span><b>Zinc Oxide h\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 trong d\u1ea1ng KCN n\u00e0o &amp; k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1i \u01b0u?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>D\u1ea1ng n\u1ec1n:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> cream, lotion, gel-cream, stick, tinted (pha s\u1eafc t\u1ed1\/iron oxides \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m white cast, b\u1ed5 sung che ph\u1ee7 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng xanh\/HEV).<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p \u201ckinh \u0111i\u1ec3n\u201d:<\/b><\/p>\n<p><b>ZnO + TiO\u2082:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> t\u0103ng UVB v\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m white cast; TiO\u2082 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng UVB t\u1ed1t, ZnO l\u00e0m t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u1edf kho\u1ea3ng UVA1\/UVA2.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Hybrid (ZnO + h\u1eefu c\u01a1 th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 c\u1ee7a h\u1eefu c\u01a1 + \u0111\u1ed9 b\u1ec1n\/ d\u1ecbu c\u1ee7a ZnO.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>ZnO + Iron Oxides:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 che HEV\/\u00e1nh xanh v\u00e0 UVA d\u00e0i, h\u1eefu \u00edch cho n\u00e1m\/PIH.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-8175 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/90-2.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/90-2.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/90-2-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/90-2-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/90-2-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"luu-y-su-dung-kem-chong-nang-co-mang-loc-zinc-oxide\"><\/span><b>L\u01b0u \u00fd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng c\u00f3 m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc Zinc Oxide<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dang-kcn-co-zinc-oxide-dung-tot-nhat-khi-nao\"><\/span><b>D\u1ea1ng KCN c\u00f3 Zinc Oxide d\u00f9ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t khi n\u00e0o?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><b>Sinh ho\u1ea1t h\u1eb1ng ng\u00e0y \u2013 da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> \u01b0u ti\u00ean ZnO\/tinted ZnO \u0111\u1ec3 v\u1eeba che v\u1eeba d\u1ecbu.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Sau th\u1ee7 thu\u1eadt (peel\/laser vi \u0111i\u1ec3m):<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> ZnO B\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng, d\u1ecbu\u2014th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c khuy\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb khi h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o da \u0111ang mong manh.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng d\u00f2ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng thu\u1ea7n v\u1eadt l\u00fd. Sau khi da b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng h\u00f3a h\u1ecdc c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng g\u00e2y t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng h\u01a1n v\u00e0 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng sau t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh PIH (t\u0103ng s\u1eafc t\u1ed1 sau vi\u00eam). <\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Xem th\u00eam: <a href=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/kem-chong-nang-vat-ly-gsc\/\">[Kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd GSC]<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>Tr\u1ebb em &amp; v\u00f9ng m\u1eaft:<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> ZnO tinh khi\u1ebft\/tinted, kh\u00f4ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u\u2014gi\u1ea3m cay m\u1eaft, an t\u00e2m h\u01a1n khi b\u00f4i d\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"co-luu-y-va-chong-chi-dinhkhong-nen-ket-hop-voi-chat-nao-khong\"><\/span><b>C\u00f3 l\u01b0u \u00fd v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh\/kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5t n\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng?<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">X\u1ecbt b\u1ed9t\/aerosol ch\u1ee9a ZnO: kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean d\u00f9ng cho tr\u1ebb em v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 b\u1ec7nh n\u1ec1n h\u00f4 h\u1ea5p, tr\u00e1nh h\u00edt ph\u1ea3i (nguy c\u01a1 h\u00f4 h\u1ea5p). D\u00f9ng cream\/lotion\/stick an to\u00e0n h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng ho\u00e1 h\u1ecdc \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh v\u1edbi m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc kh\u00e1c; v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 d\u00e0y l\u1edbp ph\u1ee7 v\u00e0 t\u00e1n x\u1ea1 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u. V\u1eady n\u00ean c\u1ea7n ch\u00fa \u00fd b\u00f4i \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1ee7 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1i kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng n\u00e0y.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">White cast\/gh\u00ea m\u1eb7t: v\u00ec h\u1ea1t ph\u00e2n t\u1eed to v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t m\u00e0u tr\u1eafng n\u00ean th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i v\u1ec7t tr\u1eafng, n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 nano \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c, th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 h\u01a1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8176\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8176\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8176 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/90-3.webp\" alt=\"Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef c\u00f3 thai v\u00e0 cho con b\u00fa c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc ZnO kh\u00f4ng?\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/90-3.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/90-3-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/90-3-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/90-3-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8176\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef c\u00f3 thai v\u00e0 cho con b\u00fa c\u00f3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00e0ng l\u1ecdc Zinc Oxide kh\u00f4ng?<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3. KCN v\u1eadt l\u00fd (ZnO\/TiO\u2082) th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn an to\u00e0n cho thai k\u1ef3 v\u00e0 cho con b\u00fa khi d\u00f9ng ngo\u00e0i da \u0111\u00fang c\u00e1ch. Lu\u00f4n thoa \u0111\u1ee7 li\u1ec1u 2 mg\/cm\u00b2, d\u1eb7m l\u1ea1i khi ra n\u1eafng l\u00e2u.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cach-thoa-lieu-luong\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch thoa &amp; li\u1ec1u l\u01b0\u1ee3ng\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<figure id=\"attachment_8177\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-8177\" style=\"width: 880px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-8177 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/90-4.webp\" alt=\"S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kcn v\u1eadt l\u00fd\" width=\"880\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/90-4.webp 880w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/90-4-300x300.webp 300w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/90-4-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/media.gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2026\/01\/90-4-600x375.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 880px) 100vw, 880px\"><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-8177\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd sao cho \u0111\u00fang v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 li\u1ec1u l\u01b0\u1ee3ng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Quy t\u1eafc \u201c\u0111i\u1ec3m \u2013 t\u00e1n \u2013 d\u1eb7m\u201d: ch\u1ea5m 10\u201312 \u0111i\u1ec3m, t\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec1u (n\u00ean v\u1ed7 kh\u00f4ng mi\u1ebft, ch\u00e0), \u0111\u1ee3i set 5\u201310 ph\u00fat; n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i v\u1ec7t tr\u1eafng \u2192 d\u00f9ng tinted ho\u1eb7c t\u00e1n th\u00eam l\u1edbp n\u1ec1n ti\u1ec7p m\u00e0u.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"bao-quan-bao-bi\"><\/span><b>B\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n &amp; bao b\u00ec\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><b>Tr\u00e1nh nhi\u1ec7t \u2013 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">, \u0111\u1eady n\u1eafp k\u00edn \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh t\u00e1ch pha.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><b>L\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u00f9ng<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> n\u1ebfu s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0 d\u1ea1ng s\u1eefa l\u1ecfng (ZnO c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1eafng).<\/span><\/p>\n<p>T\u00e0i li\u1ec7u tham kh\u1ea3o:<\/p>\n<p>Smijs, T., &amp; Pavel, S. (2011). Titanium dioxide and zinc oxide nanoparticles in sunscreens: focus on their safety and effectiveness.\u00a0<i>Nanotechnology, Science and Applications<\/i>,\u00a0<i>4<\/i>(4), 95\u2013112. <a href=\"https:\/\/doi.org\/10.2147\/nsa.s19419\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https:\/\/doi.org\/10.2147\/nsa.s19419<\/a><\/p>\n<p>\u200c<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Zinc Oxide l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a kem ch\u1ed1ng n\u1eafng v\u1eadt l\u00fd: che ph\u1ee7 UVA\/UVB \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh, dung n\u1ea1p t\u1ed1t, gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u\/solvent. <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":12,"featured_media":8178,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[13],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-8173","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-xu-huong"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8173","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/12"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=8173"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8173\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":8903,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8173\/revisions\/8903"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/8178"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=8173"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=8173"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=8173"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}